    "_postman_id": "03e633ad-87f1-4bc1-96e8-d478c1b2dd26",
    "name": "Student API",
    "description": "# Student API\n\nThe **Student API** is a RESTful service for managing student records. It provides a complete set of **CRUD** (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations, allowing clients to create new students, retrieve individual or all student records, update existing entries, and delete students by ID.\n\n## Base URL\n\n```\nhttp://localhost:8080\n\n ```\n\n## Endpoints\n\n| Method | Endpoint | Description |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| `POST` | `/api/v1/students` | Create a new student record |\n| `GET` | `/api/v1/students` | Retrieve a list of all students |\n| `GET` | `/api/v1/students/{id}` | Fetch a specific student by their ID |\n| `PUT` | `/api/v1/students/{id}` | Update an existing student's details |\n| `DELETE` | `/api/v1/students/{id}` | Remove a student record by ID |\n\n## Health Check\n\nA health check endpoint is available to verify that the service is up and running:\n\n| Method | Endpoint | Description |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| `GET` | `/healthcheck` | Returns the current health status of the API |",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "32767552"
  },
